 droughts? (2009) Geophys Res Lett, 36, pp. L04706. , doi:10.1029/2008GL036801; Verdon, D.C., Franks, S.W., Indian Ocean sea surface temperature variability and winter rainfall: Eastern Australia (2005) Water Resour Res, 41, pp. W09413. , doi:10.1029/2004WR003845; Verdon, D.C., Franks, S.W., Long-term behaviour of ENSO: interactions with the PDO over the past 400 years inferred from paleoclimate records (2006) Geophys Res Lett, 33, pp. L07612. , doi:10.1029/2005GL025052; Verdon, D.C., Wyatt, A.M., Kiem, A.S., Franks, S.W., Multidecadal variability of rainfall and streamflow: Eastern Australia (2004) Water Resour Res, 40, pp. W10201. , doi:10.1029/2004WR2003234; Verdon-Kidd, D.C., Kiem, A.S., On the relationship between large-scale climate modes and regional synoptic patterns that drive Victorian rainfall (2009) Hydrol Earth Syst Sci, 13, pp. 467-479. , www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/13/467/2009/","Chiew, F. H. S.; CSIRO Land and Water, GPO Box 1666, Canberra, ACT 2601, Australia; email: francis.chiew@csiro.au",,,,,,,,14363240,,,,"English","Stoch. Environ. Res. Risk Assess.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-79952992496
